          "id": "sequential_build",
          "label": "Each section builds on the one before it \u2014 no section reads as a standalone block disconnected from the narrative"
        }
      ],
      "priority": 3
    },
    {
      "name": "Donor as Strategic Co-Architect",
      "category": "Audience",
      "description": "Donors are framed as people who made strategic decisions that produced specific, causal outcomes \u2014 not people being asked to fill a gap or respond to need. Past contributions are named as bets on a model that produced measurable results; new asks are positioned as the next decision in an ongoing strategy.",
      "dimensions": [
        {
          "id": "past_contribution_causal",
          "label": "Past donor decisions are named as producing specific, causal outcomes \u2014 not thanked in vague or generic terms"
        },
        {
          "id": "strategic_language",
          "label": "Uses language of decisions, bets, models, and investment \u2014 not need, gaps, generosity, or charity"
        },
        {
          "id": "ask_as_continuation",
          "label": "New ask is positioned as a continuation of a strategy already in motion, not a new or separate request"
        },
        {
          "id": "specific_funding_unlocks",
          "label": "Specific funding amounts are tied to specific, concrete outcomes or unlocks \u2014 not abstract impact"
        }
      ],
      "priority": 4
    },
